article.description: E.J. Crawford had 18 points as Iona rolled past Quinnipiac 73-52 on Friday night.
article.headline: Crawford, Ross lead Iona over Quinnipiac 73-52
article.linkText: Crawford, Ross lead Iona over Quinnipiac 73-52
article.story: HAMDEN, Conn. -- E.J. Crawford had 18 points as Iona rolled past Quinnipiac 73-52 on Friday night. Isaiah Ross added 16 points for the Gaels, while Dylan van Eyck chipped in 15. Isaiah Washington had 13 points for Iona (6-12, 4-7 Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference). Matt Balanc had 14 points for the Bobcats (11-10, 6-5). Jacob Rigoni added 12 points. Rich Kelly had six assists. Iona plays Fairfield on the road on Sunday. Quinnipiac matches up against Manhattan at home on Sunday. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
